item.title: The Moscow Ripper Casefile: Transition and Reaction
item.description:
Now that Bryan Kohberger has been arrested and charged in the murders of the #IdahoStudents, I open the Moscow Ripper casefile. A series of episodes that will dig deep into the crime, the evidence, a possible motive and the reality of the death penalty. This episode is about the transition and the reaction. The cause and effect. The 2500 miles west that brought us here. Next, I give you my reasons. #BryanKohberger

Follow DV for new episodes each week... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/15a4788c/podcast/rss
